	Will you people with web-based or GUI-based E-mail clients *please*
observe the following plaintext ettiquette rules?

(1)	turn off HTML
(2)	turn off vcards
(3)	turn off images in your .signature
(4)	don't send any kinds of binary attachments

	Vielen Dank,

